sub_title: PhD student in Chemistry at University of Amsterdam
summary:
Currently finishing a PhD in physical chemistry focused on mechanistic investigations of highly sensitive frustrated Lewis pair systems.

Highly interested in how molecular structure affects physical properties of materials.
Appreciates combining experimental work with in-depth computer modelling to thoroughly understand complex systems.
